



World sim mode stuff:
- Every piece of ore can be smelted/refined into x talents/pounds/grams of the material it's an ore of.
- Number of talets/pounds/grams depends on the size of the ore, which is determined randomally according to its properties in the config files.
- All items/buildings/vehicles use x talents/pounds/grams of that material.
- There are different types of ore for different types of materials.
